   UNDER CONSTRUCTION
   I-405 and SR167 interchange construction
   I-405 and SR 167 Interchange
   This project will improve the interchange at I-405 and SR 167 and
   reduce congestion on southbound I-405 and northbound SR 167 during
   non-peak hours.
